Dialogue: 0,0:00:01.96,0:00:03.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我的名字叫本須和秀樹
Dialogue: 0,0:00:04.60,0:00:06.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,今年生日過後就滿19歲
Dialogue: 0,0:00:06.97,0:00:08.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,現在是18歲
Dialogue: 0,0:00:09.00,0:00:11.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,今年春天預定到東京唸大學
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.38,0:00:49.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,來了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:01.52,0:01:03.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,沒錯，正式成為大學生…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:03.83,0:01:05.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,本來應該是這樣的
Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.90,0:01:11.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,落榜了！
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.50,0:01:12.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,沒考上！
Dialogue: 0,0:01:12.93,0:01:14.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,得重考了！
Dialogue: 0,0:01:17.87,0:01:19.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,既然如此，我就去補習班
Dialogue: 0,0:01:19.21,0:01:20.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,到補習班努力用功
Dialogue: 0,0:01:20.71,0:01:22.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,明年我一定考上給你看
Dialogue: 0,0:01:22.84,0:01:25.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,對了，既然要去就去東京吧
Dialogue: 0,0:01:25.71,0:01:27.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,反正想唸的學校也在東京
Dialogue: 0,0:01:27.88,0:01:28.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,對吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:01:28.95,0:01:33.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好，我要去東京！
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.88,0:03:27.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,ちぃ，甦醒
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.02,0:03:30.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,終於到了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.76,0:03:32.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真不愧是東京
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.13,0:03:34.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不論到哪裡都好多人啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.00,0:03:37.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我看看，公寓是在…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.84,0:03:44.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,距離目的地約45分鐘
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.27,0:03:47.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,在池袋換車，然後…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.74,0:03:50.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是電腦耶
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.58,0:03:53.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我第一次親眼看到
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.62,0:03:58.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,最近這個時代\NIT 科技與網際網路之類的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.02,0:04:00.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,變得相當發達
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.79,0:04:03.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,生活似乎變得非常便利
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.66,0:04:06.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,其中最厲害的就是這種電腦
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.73,0:04:08.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,做得像真人一樣
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.06,0:04:11.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,雖然我不太懂
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.07,0:04:14.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但聽說它有很多不同的功能
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.27,0:04:16.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我家住的鄉下地方
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.61,0:04:19.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,根本就沒人有電腦
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.34,0:04:20.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好棒喔，好棒喔，電腦
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.91,0:04:23.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好想要喔，好想要喔
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.58,0:04:28.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這種價錢我怎麼可能買得起
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.85,0:04:29.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,在表演嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.72,0:04:30.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那個人是怎麼回事？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.59,0:04:31.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,因為春天到了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.35,0:04:32.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,媽媽
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.32,0:04:33.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不可以看他
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.67,0:04:47.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真的好丟臉喔
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.17,0:04:50.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,得把自言自語的習慣改掉才行
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.94,0:04:54.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,畢竟至今為止\N我身邊盡是些牛啊馬的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.75,0:05:03.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不過電腦真的好像人類
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.92,0:05:06.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,而且又那麼的可愛
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.46,0:05:10.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但也未免太貴了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.29,0:05:13.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,世人對這件事都沒意見嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.70,0:05:16.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,難道說都市人都很有錢嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.40,0:05:18.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,所以貧窮的重考生不准買？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.93,0:05:20.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是這樣的嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.60,0:05:22.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可惡
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.17,0:05:24.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我也好想買台電腦
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.17,0:05:25.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好想收發郵件
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.34,0:05:28.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好想看網路的色情網站
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.78,0:05:29.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,色情？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.81,0:05:33.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不是…那個…這是…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.22,0:05:36.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,在這樣的美女面前
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.15,0:05:38.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我竟然如此失態
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.45,0:05:40.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,啊，對了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.02,0:05:43.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我正在找一棟公寓
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.16,0:05:45.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,請問妳有聽過嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.23,0:05:48.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,它的名字很奇怪\N叫作“ GAB 城崎”
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.90,0:05:50.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這裡就是
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.80,0:05:54.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這裡就是“ GAB 城崎”
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.57,0:05:56.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,啊，就是這裡啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.24,0:06:04.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,您就是本須和秀樹先生吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.41,0:06:05.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是…是的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.68,0:06:09.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我是這裡的管理員\N日比谷千歲
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.62,0:06:11.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就是這裡
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.69,0:06:12.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.19,0:06:16.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,自來水跟瓦斯馬上都能用
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.06,0:06:19.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,總開關在這上面
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.09,0:06:20.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好窄喔
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.20,0:06:21.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不過也是沒辦法的事
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.76,0:06:23.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,租金一個月才兩萬…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.73,0:06:27.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,送達的行李\N已經先幫您搬進房間了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.04,0:06:29.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不知道這樣可以嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.30,0:06:31.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好的，謝謝妳
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.47,0:06:33.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不過應該很重吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.81,0:06:35.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,箱子這麼多
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.41,0:06:36.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真是不好意思
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.45,0:06:37.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,別客氣
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.68,0:06:40.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,因為幫您搬進來的是新保先生
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.68,0:06:42.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,新保先生？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.28,0:06:45.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他差不多也回來了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.72,0:06:48.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他住在隔壁的204號房
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.49,0:06:49.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是這樣的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.69,0:06:51.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,待會兒得謝謝他才行
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.46,0:06:54.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那麼，以後請多多指教
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.33,0:06:55.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我才要請妳多多指教
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.73,0:06:56.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.93,0:06:58.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.24,0:07:03.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真是個超漂亮的管理員
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.61,0:07:06.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,她說她住在101號房
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.31,0:07:08.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,能住進這麼漂亮的人住的公寓
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.68,0:07:10.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,搞不好我真的很走運
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.28,0:07:13.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,來了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.68,0:07:15.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,難道是管理員小姐嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.42,0:07:18.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,來了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.76,0:07:27.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,恭喜你，恭喜你
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.96,0:07:30.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,恭喜你搬家
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.20,0:07:32.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這是啥玩意啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.30,0:07:36.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Master ，這個人好可怕喔
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.54,0:07:37.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉，抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.44,0:07:38.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,嚇到你了是嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.44,0:07:40.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,請…請問…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.51,0:07:42.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,初次見面
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.61,0:07:44.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我叫新保弘
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.35,0:07:47.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我是住在隔壁204號房的房客
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.82,0:07:49.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是你幫我搬行李的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.58,0:07:50.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,沒錯
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.49,0:07:51.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,新保先生
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.75,0:07:53.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真是謝謝你
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.22,0:07:54.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,叫我新保就行了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.66,0:07:56.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,別用敬語啦
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.12,0:07:57.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你幾歲？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.76,0:07:58.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,18
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.63,0:07:59.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,跟我一樣嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.73,0:08:01.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,18？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.73,0:08:05.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,然後你下禮拜就要去唸\N“關補習班”對吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.87,0:08:06.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我也是
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.94,0:08:08.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,落榜二人組
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.67,0:08:09.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真的假的？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.50,0:08:10.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真的，真的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.51,0:08:11.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,請多指教
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.61,0:08:15.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那，這是什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.04,0:08:17.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這是我的電腦
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.41,0:08:18.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好小喔
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.68,0:08:20.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,因為是攜帶式的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.65,0:08:22.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,打招呼
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.72,0:08:23.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.75,0:08:27.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我叫絲茉茉，請多指教
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.16,0:08:29.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好棒喔，好棒喔
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.26,0:08:31.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好可怕
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.03,0:08:34.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼啦\N你的反應太誇張了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.26,0:08:35.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你沒有攜帶式電腦嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.86,0:08:38.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,應該說是，我連電腦都沒有
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.70,0:08:40.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,在這種時代，你的確很罕見
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.80,0:08:43.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,而且就算買了我也不會用
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.04,0:08:46.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這東西只要打開開關就會動的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.48,0:08:48.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,剩下的事， OS 會自己幫你做
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.88,0:08:49.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你懂得還真多
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.98,0:08:50.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你很熟這東西是嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.95,0:08:52.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,普通啦
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.08,0:08:53.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,電腦真的很棒嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.78,0:08:54.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那當然
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.82,0:08:56.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可以用絲茉茉打電話
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.79,0:08:58.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,也可以收郵件
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.69,0:08:59.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可以上網嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.86,0:09:00.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.59,0:09:02.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,當然也可以上色情網站
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.79,0:09:05.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是嗎，也可以上色情網站啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.39,0:09:07.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,色情網站算是基本的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.63,0:09:11.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,色情網站，色情網…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.13,0:09:13.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,需要加熱嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.60,0:09:14.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.00,0:09:16.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.44,0:09:18.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,熱好了之後我會通知您
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.71,0:09:20.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,請您稍坐片刻
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.94,0:09:22.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.18,0:09:25.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝光臨
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.62,0:09:29.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,話說回來\N電腦真的好厲害啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.58,0:09:31.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,連收銀機都會用
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.69,0:09:34.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,新保那台好像是叫作絲茉茉吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.39,0:09:36.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,原來也有那麼小台的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.69,0:09:39.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他說也能用來打電話
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.09,0:09:40.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好好喔
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.83,0:09:46.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,想要歸想要\N不過實在太貴了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.54,0:09:49.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,況且我到現在\N連電腦的“電”字都不懂
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.11,0:09:52.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,到底要拿來做些什麼\N我完全不知道
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.77,0:09:55.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,色情網站我是會去看啦
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.15,0:09:58.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好好喔，電腦
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.75,0:10:00.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,既然都已經做成人型  的了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.62,0:10:04.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那種長得非常可愛的\N不知道有沒有掉在路上
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.39,0:10:06.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這是不可能的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.33,0:10:23.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,啊，有人死掉了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.70,0:10:24.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是殺人嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.47,0:10:25.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這是殺人嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.31,0:10:26.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這算是殺人事件嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.01,0:10:28.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼回事？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.84,0:10:31.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,剛搬到東京第一天\N就被捲進了殺人事件嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.58,0:10:32.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,讓我想想
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.51,0:10:33.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,遇到這種情況該怎麼做？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.85,0:10:34.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,該先做什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.85,0:10:36.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,叫警察？還是叫救護車？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.68,0:10:38.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我想想…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.85,0:10:40.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那對耳朵…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.39,0:10:44.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那好像跟我今天\N在車站前電器行看到的一樣
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.79,0:10:48.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,搞什麼，別嚇我啦
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.09,0:10:51.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,害我以為是什麼\N懸疑殺人事件呢
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.97,0:10:54.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真是的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.64,0:10:56.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,還是快點回去
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.74,0:10:58.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,把房間整理整理好了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.97,0:11:00.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,等等
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.74,0:11:02.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這是電腦
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.94,0:11:05.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,然後這裡是垃圾場
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.11,0:11:07.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,也就是說，這個…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.58,0:11:09.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,應該是垃圾吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.22,0:11:10.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這麼說來
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.28,0:11:11.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我拿走這個也無所謂吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.05,0:11:12.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可以吧？可以吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.79,0:11:13.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可以吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.15,0:11:16.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,話說回來，產業廢棄物這些東西
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.39,0:11:17.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,應該是越少越好才對吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.06,0:11:19.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,因為會產生戴奧辛之類的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.06,0:11:22.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,二氧化碳也會破壞臭氧層
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.16,0:11:25.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好重啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.51,0:11:41.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這…這就是電腦的重量嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.72,0:11:45.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,重的要死
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.03,0:12:00.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,原來電腦這麼重啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.07,0:12:01.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我懂了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.93,0:12:03.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,人家說開機很重或很輕鬆\N（日文“開機很重”意指“很慢”）
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.77,0:12:05.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,原來是這麼回事啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.17,0:12:07.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,聽新保說他那台很輕鬆
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.71,0:12:10.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,看來攜帶式真的很輕
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.15,0:12:19.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不過看她這個樣子
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.45,0:12:22.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,跟人類女孩沒什麼兩樣嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.62,0:12:25.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,又漂亮
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.76,0:12:28.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,又柔軟
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.36,0:12:34.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這應該還很新吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.67,0:12:36.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是因為買了新機種\N所以才被丟掉的嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.74,0:12:38.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真是可惜
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.54,0:12:41.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我會好好地物盡其用的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.84,0:12:44.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好，快來用看看吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.11,0:12:45.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我想想，該怎麼做呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.45,0:12:47.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我記得新保說過\N只要按 下開關就會動了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.98,0:12:52.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,開關，開關，開關，開關，開關
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.92,0:12:54.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,在哪裡？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.85,0:12:56.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,搞不懂
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.52,0:12:58.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,開關在哪裡啊？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.69,0:13:01.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,已經沒有地方可以按了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.13,0:13:01.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這裡也按了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.06,0:13:02.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這裡也按了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.03,0:13:03.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這裡也按了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.96,0:13:05.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這裡也按了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.60,0:13:06.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這裡也按了…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.03,0:13:09.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我把突起的部份全按遍了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.60,0:13:10.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,全部
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.20,0:13:12.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,全部…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.94,0:13:16.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,難道…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.84,0:13:18.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,在這裡面？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.15,0:13:21.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼可能
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.98,0:13:23.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼可能會有這種事
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.68,0:13:26.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但是只差那裡沒按 過…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.86,0:13:38.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我可沒有什麼下流的念頭喔
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.03,0:13:40.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,如果不會動的話\N我會很困擾的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.67,0:13:42.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,如果不會動的話
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.17,0:13:45.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是…是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.24,0:13:48.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,對吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.86,0:15:18.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,ちぃ？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.50,0:15:21.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,ちぃ？什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.20,0:15:23.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,ちぃ
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.64,0:15:25.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,ちぃ？是什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.87,0:15:28.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那是妳的名字嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.18,0:15:30.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,ちぃ
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.24,0:15:31.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,等一下
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.11,0:15:32.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼回事？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.38,0:15:33.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,究竟是怎麼了？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.65,0:15:35.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這台電腦雖然勉強動了起來
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.98,0:15:37.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但是除了“ちぃ”之外\N什麼都不會講
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.42,0:15:38.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,全身赤裸
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.32,0:15:40.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,然後又非常的可愛
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.29,0:15:42.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,ちぃ
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.29,0:15:45.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,有，我有看過這種場景
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.06,0:15:46.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,在路上撿到
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.03,0:15:49.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,或是突然闖進一個\N很可愛的女孩
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.00,0:15:51.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,有著不可思議的力量
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.63,0:15:52.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,什麼事都會做
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.70,0:15:55.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,甚至還愛上一起同居的男人
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.30,0:15:57.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,什麼事都幫忙做
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.47,0:15:58.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不論是煮菜、打掃
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.97,0:16:00.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,或是那方面的事
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.21,0:16:02.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,ちぃ？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.48,0:16:04.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我果然太走運了嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.45,0:16:07.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,來了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.05,0:16:08.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我是新保
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.95,0:16:10.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,要不要去洗澡？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.28,0:16:13.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我平常都去附近健康中心的澡堂
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.15,0:16:15.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你也知道吧\N因為這公寓沒有浴室嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.22,0:16:17.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,喔，我知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.59,0:16:18.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你能馬上出門嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.59,0:16:19.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我馬上幫你開門
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.76,0:16:21.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,喂…全身裸體！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.89,0:16:22.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那是理所當然的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.86,0:16:24.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,因為要去洗澡啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.20,0:16:25.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,還是說什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.26,0:16:27.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,難道你是那種\N不穿泳褲就不敢洗的人嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.60,0:16:28.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,ちぃ
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.23,0:16:30.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,啊，沒有，沒什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.14,0:16:30.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不太妙吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.04,0:16:32.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這種狀況實在不太妙吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.84,0:16:33.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,ちぃ
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.78,0:16:36.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,衣服，衣服
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.94,0:16:37.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,有沒有什麼衣服，可以穿的東西
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.08,0:16:41.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,沒有，沒有，沒有，沒有
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.38,0:16:44.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,早知道應該在箱子寫上\N裡面裝的是什麼東西
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.82,0:16:45.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,啊，是毛巾啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.82,0:16:47.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不過暫時先…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.49,0:16:48.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,ちぃ
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.02,0:16:50.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,看…看起來更性感了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.76,0:16:52.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,喂，還沒好嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.29,0:16:56.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,再找件能穿的，能穿的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.96,0:16:57.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,討厭
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.86,0:16:58.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不是啦
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.97,0:17:00.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼了？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.40,0:17:02.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你找不到要帶去澡堂的東西嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.17,0:17:03.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不是啦
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.20,0:17:04.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,要我幫忙嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.00,0:17:06.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不，沒關係
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.57,0:17:07.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不用客氣啦
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.74,0:17:09.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,奇怪，門沒鎖嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.58,0:17:11.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我忘了鎖門
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.31,0:17:13.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,總之，先把她藏起來…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.31,0:17:14.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,很好
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.28,0:17:16.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我要進去了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.52,0:17:18.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,哇，怎麼回事啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.22,0:17:20.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,房間怎麼弄得亂七八糟
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.25,0:17:21.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你不用那麼著急
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.62,0:17:23.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,反正澡堂開到12點
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.99,0:17:25.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,嗯？怎麼了？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.86,0:17:26.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你流鼻血了耶
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.89,0:17:28.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不要緊，不要緊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.66,0:17:30.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我只是稍微跌了一跤
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.30,0:17:31.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.43,0:17:34.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可是要找洗髮精之類的\N應該很困難吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.10,0:17:35.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我的借你用吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.80,0:17:36.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.74,0:17:37.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,毛巾呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.60,0:17:38.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,毛巾我有
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.94,0:17:40.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,啊，不是，雖然有
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.81,0:17:42.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不過正在使用中
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.58,0:17:43.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你在說什麼啊？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.18,0:17:45.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,別在意，別在意
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.34,0:17:46.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我在自言自語
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.48,0:17:48.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,算了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.78,0:17:49.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我會在房裡
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.02,0:17:51.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,如果你準備好了，就來叫我吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.85,0:17:52.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,喔，我知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.82,0:17:53.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我馬上就過去
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.15,0:17:55.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那我走了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.36,0:18:00.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,ちぃ
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.70,0:18:03.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,還有啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.13,0:18:04.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,什麼事？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.36,0:18:06.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你在幹嘛？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.43,0:18:07.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,沒有，那個…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.63,0:18:08.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我又跌了一跤
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.70,0:18:10.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你還好吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.20,0:18:10.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,ちぃ
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.74,0:18:12.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,有…有什麼事嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.31,0:18:15.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,如果你沒有換洗的衣物\N我的可以借你穿
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.41,0:18:16.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,ちぃ
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.18,0:18:17.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,沒關係，沒關係
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.28,0:18:18.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我有帶來
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.68,0:18:20.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我馬上就過去\N你回房裡等我吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.51,0:18:21.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好嗎？好嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.85,0:18:24.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.26,0:18:33.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我還有事忘了講
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.43,0:18:34.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.99,0:18:36.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,別嚇我啦
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.76,0:18:37.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉，抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.70,0:18:38.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,什麼事？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.30,0:18:42.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,澡堂的費用要400円
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.10,0:18:44.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,如果要用三溫暖\N還要再加300円
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.80,0:18:45.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是嗎？我知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.04,0:18:47.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝你
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.41,0:18:53.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,ちぃ？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.45,0:19:00.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,唉，好累喔
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.89,0:19:02.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,ちぃ
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.36,0:19:09.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,待在這裡不要動，知道了嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.90,0:19:12.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,ちぃ
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.27,0:19:15.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,新保啊，你可不可以不要…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.70,0:19:17.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,管理員小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.70,0:19:20.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,有…有什麼事嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.77,0:19:23.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這是牛蒡
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.11,0:19:24.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,如果您不討厭的話…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.04,0:19:26.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,咦？給我的嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.71,0:19:27.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.55,0:19:30.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,哇，謝謝妳
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.22,0:19:31.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我煮太多了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.05,0:19:33.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,如果不會造成您困擾的話
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.82,0:19:35.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,哪有什麼困擾
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.52,0:19:36.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,沒這回事
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.46,0:19:37.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,一點都沒有問題
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.02,0:19:39.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.46,0:19:40.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,下次如果我還有做什麼好吃的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.06,0:19:42.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我再拿來給您吃
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.03,0:19:44.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真的嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.26,0:19:46.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,嗯，如果您不嫌棄的話
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.60,0:19:49.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我好高興
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.40,0:19:51.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真是謝謝妳
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.11,0:19:54.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,幫了我一個大忙
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.61,0:19:56.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,太感動了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.38,0:19:58.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,太棒了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.51,0:20:02.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,ちぃ？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.38,0:20:03.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,哎呀，哎呀
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.42,0:20:04.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,啊，不是的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.68,0:20:06.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那是電腦
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.42,0:20:09.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真是可愛的電腦小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.49,0:20:12.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不是的，那是電腦\N所以…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.39,0:20:15.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那麼本須和先生，電腦小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.49,0:20:16.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,晚安
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.06,0:20:18.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,ちぃ
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.83,0:20:24.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,管…管理員小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.54,0:20:28.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,唉，她一定認為我是變態
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.64,0:20:32.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,以為我把電腦的衣服脫光\N然後一個人在暗爽
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.88,0:20:34.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好…好好吃
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.91,0:20:36.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,咦？不去澡堂了？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.65,0:20:37.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.55,0:20:38.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.62,0:20:41.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,因為想在今天把房間整理好
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.02,0:20:42.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這樣啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.76,0:20:44.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,算了，那就沒辦法了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.42,0:20:45.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真的很抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.86,0:20:46.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,沒關係啦
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.99,0:20:48.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不用那麼在意啦
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.13,0:20:55.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,ちぃ
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.07,0:20:56.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,很好
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.74,0:20:59.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,ちぃ
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.27,0:21:00.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我在慌什麼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.67,0:21:01.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,對方只是電腦
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.94,0:21:06.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,冷靜點…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.25,0:21:07.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,ちぃ
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.95,0:21:10.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我問妳
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.18,0:21:11.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,ちぃ？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.62,0:21:13.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,妳只會說“ちぃ”嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.65,0:21:14.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,ちぃ
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.73,0:21:19.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,畢竟是在垃圾場撿來的電腦
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.73,0:21:22.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,嗯…該不會是哪裡壞了吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.88,0:21:42.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,別露出那種表情啦
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.05,0:21:46.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,妳是在想說\N自己又要被丟掉了嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.39,0:21:51.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,既然都把妳撿回來了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.06,0:21:53.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我會好好愛惜妳的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:56.10,0:21:57.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,ちぃ
Dialogue: 0,0:22:01.93,0:22:04.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但是，真的好可愛
Dialogue: 0,0:22:04.94,0:22:07.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,滑嫩嫩的，暖呼呼的
Dialogue: 0,0:22:07.94,0:22:09.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,如果沒有這對耳朵
Dialogue: 0,0:22:09.28,0:22:11.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,簡直就像是普通的女孩
Dialogue: 0,0:22:16.78,0:22:18.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,胸部也好軟…
Dialogue: 0,0:23:55.71,0:23:57.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,能撿到這麼可愛的電腦
Dialogue: 0,0:23:57.72,0:23:59.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我真是超幸運啊
Dialogue: 0,0:23:59.28,0:24:00.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,ちぃ，ちぃ
Dialogue: 0,0:24:00.45,0:24:03.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但是她只會說“ちぃ”
Dialogue: 0,0:24:03.26,0:24:05.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是哪裡故障了嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:24:05.12,0:24:07.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我也完全不懂
Dialogue: 0,0:24:07.23,0:24:09.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,ちぃ
Dialogue: 0,0:24:09.09,0:24:10.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不過，不用擔心
Dialogue: 0,0:24:10.93,0:24:14.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,只要到新保介紹的\N那個很懂電腦的人家裡
Dialogue: 0,0:24:14.20,0:24:15.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,或許可以知道些什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:24:15.63,0:24:17.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,ちぃ
Dialogue: 0,0:24:17.50,0:24:20.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Chobits 下一回\N「ちぃ，出門」
Dialogue: 0,0:24:20.91,0:24:21.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,咦？
Dialogue: 0,0:24:21.57,0:24:24.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,網路上的都市傳說？
